data.description: OPEN HOUSE 5/8 12pm - 3pm.   Great Location! Enjoy the Forest Hammock amenities & fabulous schools w/out the CDD fee! Interior features a split floorplan, updated lighting & plumbing fixtures, wood laminate & tile w/ carpeted BR's, kitchen w/ plenty of cabinetry, counterspace & breakfast bar, modern barn door leading to nice-sized master bath w/ walk-in shower & large closet & more. Exterior features a screened lanai leading to a private & peaceful partially-fenced preserve backyard, partially guttered, & an add'l open patio. Amenities include a pool, playground, volleyball & tennis courts as well as a multi-purpose field. Easy access to NAS Jax, Highways, Towncenter dining & shopping & Epic Movie Theater! Transferrable Termite Bond & more. Come see for yourself. You won't be disappointed! disappointed!
